<div style="padding:0px 0px 6px 0px"><table class="tborder" cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" align="center"><tr><td class="thead" style="font-weight:normal" ><a name="post8386"><img class="inlineimg" src="images/tdg/statusicon/post_old.gif" alt="Old" border="0" /></a> 06-12-2003, 03:55 PM</td><td class="thead" style="font-weight:normal" align="right">&nbsp;#<a href="showpost.php?s=0ae560748df707a3dc376beb25709ebc&amp;p=8386&amp;postcount=1" target="new"><strong>1</strong></a></td></tr><tr valign="top"><td class="alt2" width="175"><div id="postmenu_8386">Demasia</div><div class="smallfont">Guest</div><div class="smallfont">&nbsp;<br /><div>Posts: n/a</div><div>   </div></div></td><td class="alt1"><div class="smallfont"> 	<strong>Issue with xp loss and corpse recovery: Brainstorming</strong></div><hr size="1" style="color:" /><div><br /> Having begun with a title that is less provactive, this is an attempt to allow free thinking and constructive development of ideas.<br />
<br />
Not everyone agrees that there is a problem with Rezzes in the game.  That dissention is duly noted and respected.  However, there are many of us who do see Rezzes as problematic to the grouping dynamics in the game to varying degrees.  This thread is for those who have ideas, those who would want to help refine ideas, those who are curious and for the trolls who refuse to respect and will try to derail the constructive nature of this thread.  Feel free to preface your ideas with the reason your idea would be beneficial and even what you think the would be outcome of implementing your idea.<br />
<br />
As with any brainstorming exercise, noone is asking for every idea to be implemented.<br />
<br />
I will try to maintain a table of contents on this first page as best I can.<br />
<br />
<strong>-Updated Succor</strong> Page 1<br />
<strong>-Rez Rods</strong>  Page 1<br />
<strong>-Rez Spell for Druids</strong> Page 1<br />
<strong>-Succor of Intervention?</strong> Page 1<br />
<strong>-Preservation Spell</strong> Page 1<br />
<strong>-Summon Corpse</strong> Page 1<br />
<strong>-Outdoor Only Rez</strong> Page 1<br />
<strong>-Group Rez</strong> Page 1<br />
<strong>-Rework Necro Rezzes</strong> Page 1<br />
<strong>-GY and Zoneline Rez</strong> Page 1<br />
<strong>-Reincarnation</strong> Page 2<br />
<strong>-Summon Group</strong> Page 2<br />
<strong>-Shrines</strong> Page 3<br />
<strong>-Racial Restoration</strong> Page 3<br />
<strong>-Necro Tradeskill Item</strong> Page 3<br />
<strong>-Druid Group Life Pact?</strong> Page 3<br />
<strong>-Import Dead</strong> Page 3<br />
<strong>-Vessel of Preservation</strong> Page 4<br />
<strong>-Increase Rez Timer for 60+</strong> Page 5<br />
<strong>-Change Exp Lost At Death</strong> Page 5<br />
<strong>-DAOC style</strong> Other thread <br /></div></td></tr><tr><td class="alt2"> 	 &nbsp;</td><td class="alt1" align="right"><a href="newreply.php?s=0ae560748df707a3dc376beb25709ebc&amp;do=newreply&amp;p=8386"><img src="images/tdg/buttons/quote.gif" alt="Reply With Quote" border="0" /></a> 	</td></tr></table><div class="vbmenu_popup" id="postmenu_8386_menu" style="display:none"><table cellpadding="4" cellspacing="1" border="0"><tr><td class="thead">Demasia</td></tr></table></div></div>
