<br />
We honestly don't want a rez.  You say you do not want your invis/lev/eb "potion" abitilites.  But you would the minute you needed them.<br />
<br />
I don't know what to tell you.  They already have a class without those potion abilities, with the ability to run fast and travel through PoP portals.  This class is called a cleric.<br />
<br />
Look, you are willing to give up alot of druidical powers to be able to rez.  I'm not trying to be mean,but you honestly want to be a cleric.  I'm serious.  You really want to be one.<br />
<br />
We don't mind you wanting to be a cleric.  No one is really insulted.  But the majority of us are druids because we don't want to be clerics.  Alot of us agree, yes, there must be something you can do to make us more wanted in a group.  But it is not rez.  <br />
<br />
But please, please, please, if you want to speak for the druid class, speak for all of us, not for you.<br />
<br />
Oh, I play on Morell Thule.  I'll power level you a cleric if you'd like.  Druids are good at that.<br />
